quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  53,1,"Alla woondirii hoodere sinde fukkiima."
  53,2,"Nelaa…óo-yo o his- oo√±aaki gaa e laawol peewal, o wonaani bew…óo, kono ko o peew…óo."
  53,3,"O haalatah e o quraana tawa hombo rewi e belaa…óe makko."
  53,4,"O quraana mbo wonah si wonah wahyu, mbo Alla wahyato faade e makko ummaade e Jibriil."
  53,5,"Ko malayka jom semmbe oon woni Jibriil anndini …óum mbo."
  53,6,"E jibriil-yo o his- jom mbaadi njoo…óndi, o fotondiri e mu, hombo feenyani annabi-yo o his- e mbaadi ndi Alla tagri mbo."
  53,7,"Jibriir hombo e jookli toow…ói."
  53,8,"Refti Jibriir …ìadii o …ìeydi …ìattaade."
  53,9,"O …ìadinoo mbo fotde laanye …ói…óe wolla ko …ìuri …ìadaade."
  53,10,"Jibriir wahyii faade e maccu…óo Alla muhamadu-yo o his- ko O wahyii ko."
  53,11,"…ìernde muhamadu -yo o his- fennaani ko O yi*i ko."
  53,12,"mbela ho…óon njeddandira e makko-onon heefaree…ìe-ko Alla holli mbo ko √±ande jemma israa mbo Alla nawi mbo?"
  53,13,"Ko goonga tigi muhamadu-yo o his- yi*ii e mbaadi makko laawol go…óngol e jemma israa he."
  53,14,"ka lekki sidra haa…ótirki, kiin ka lekki mawki to kammu jee…ói…ìo."
  53,15,"ka kiin lekki woni aljanna ko…óir…óo."
  53,16,"Nde naati e sidra-Jaa…ìi- he huunde mawnde ummaade e jamirooje Alla, hay gooto anndah no …óuum laatarii si wonah Alla."
  53,17,"Yitere Nelaa…óo-yo o his- oo√±aaki nyaama wolla nana, nde yawtaani keerol."
  53,18,"Muhamadu-yo o his- yi*ii jemma seteede mbo MiiraaJ kaawisaaji Alla maw…ói kollirooji kattane Makko, O yi*i aljanna e yiite e go…ó…óum."
  53,19,"Mbela on nji*ii-onon heeferee…ìe- sanamuuji ndewaton …ói ko aldah e Alla:Laata e Ujjaa."
  53,20,"E manaata tat…ìiija go…ó…óo o e sanamuuji mon. kabree kam mbela ho…ìe njoganii on nafoore wolla lorla."
  53,21,"Mbela na woodani on-onon heefer…ìe- gorko ko yi…ó…óon ko, na woodani Mboko Joomiraawo demmbo mbo ngan√±…óon o?"
  53,22,"Ndeen fecccoore nde peccir…óon belaa…óe mon ko nde too√±nde."
  53,23,"…ói sanamuuji …ói ngonah si wonah in…óe …óe ngalah maana, …ói ngalah hay ge…óal e sifaaji Alliyankeewal on innirii…ói onon e baabiraave mon ummaade e ko*e mon, Alla jippinaani heen hay daliil, sirku…ìe …ìe ndewata si wonah sikke e belaa…óe pittaali mum en e ko seytaane su…ói e …ìer…óe mum en, arii e mum en ummaade e Joom mum en peewal e …óemngal nelaa…óo-yo o his- te …ìe peewaani."
  53,24,"Mbela na woodani ne…ó…óa ko o woo…óa ko e tefnga sanamuuji faade Alla?"
  53,25,"Alah, alanah mbo ko o woo…óa ko, ko Alla tan woodani ko sakkati e ko adii, O okka heen ko O wela O ha…óa ko O haaja."
  53,26,"Hono foti malayka nder kammuuji …ói tefoore majji nafatah hay huunde so…ói faalaama tefande gooto si wonah caggal de Alla sakkiti tefnga wonande Mbo O haaja e …ìeen, O wele tefnantee…óo o, Alla sakkitantah oon ba…óan…óo Mbo nandadiijo, O weletaake oon tefnantee…óo dewoowo ko wonah Alla."